A vast interconnected web of glowing nodes and pathways floating within a translucent corporate building structure, rendered in cyberpunk style with neon teal and magenta accents against deep purple shadows. The nodes pulse with energy, some larger hubs branching into smaller clusters, suggesting organic human connections within a digital framework. Holographic data streams flow between connection points like bioluminescent rivers. The architecture has a futuristic Singapore skyline silhouette visible through rain-streaked windows, with reflections creating depth. The mood is dynamic and transformative, suggesting evolution and reimagining of digital spaces.
